name: Ludmilla El Golilla - Classic Vers.
description:
Ludmilla is a primate that loves to change look and to get crazy when the music hits! This is the All-Star Classic NFT of a ongoing collection, with it we want to raise awareness for the beauty of different characters and styles we have on this loco planet!


3D Sculpting | Rendering | Hair Simulation | mp4 loop 1280x1280px | MUSIC
